subtitleNullable: Analyze website and URL structure of various websites
descriptionNullable:
A set of XML sitemaps for various websites.

Sitemaps are in CSV format, and can easily be obtained by using the [advertools](https://github.com/eliasdabbas/advertools) function [`sitemap_to_df`](https://advertools.readthedocs.io/en/master/advertools.sitemaps.html).

You can either supply a sitemap URL (regular sitemap or sitemap index), or a robots.txt file URL, and the function extracts all sitemaps recursively.
